These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, radish, lemon
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, teacher, scientist
1. the person eating kale is in an even position##4
2. the police-officer is on the left or right of the scientist##3
3. the police-officer is the person eating radish##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
5. the teacher is the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | lemon | kale | radish |
| Job    | teacher    | scientist | police-officer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, skydiving, sudoku
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, snowmobile
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | skydiving | sudoku | woodworking |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | jet-ski     | airplane        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, skydiving, writing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, house, indie
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | writing     | skydiving | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | house | metal     | indie  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, thriller, western
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, sailing, badminton
1. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is sailing##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | thriller  | documentary  |
| Sport         | parkour  | sailing | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, photography, woodworking
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, american, chinese
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the italian##2
2. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4
3. the chinese is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks   | woodworking | photography    |
| Nationality   | american | chinese     | italian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: dancing, video-games, singing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, surfing, ice-hockey
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | video-games | singing | dancing   |
| Sport   | ice-hockey     | cycling    | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, disaster, fantasy
3 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, pony
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is between the owner of the pony and the person watching fantasy movies##2
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | western | disaster |
| Pet           | fish         | ferret         | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: potato, apricot, apple
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, horse
1. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the goldfish and the person eating potato##2
2. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | apricot | apple | potato |
| Pet    | goldfish    | dog | horse     |

