.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, folk, disco
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, handball, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the fan of pop##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the fan of folk##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | folk  | pop  |
| Sport         | sailing | handball | skateboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, juice
There 3 different types of food: kale, mango, pepper
1. the person eating kale is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk    | juice      | milk |
| Food       | mango | pepper | kale   |

