.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, entrepreneur, musician
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, bike, ship
1. the musician is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is the pilot##1
3. the person driving the ship is the musician##1
4. the musician is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | entrepreneur | musician | pilot |
| Transport   | bike | ship   | quad-bike |

