The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, snowmobile, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
2. the french is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the mexican##3
4. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
