.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: filmmaking, dancing, sudoku
3 different pets are kept: lizard, frog, guinea-pig
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the owner of the frog##2
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | dancing | sudoku | filmmaking |
| Pet     | lizard    | guinea-pig  | frog   |

