.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, satire, zombie
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, salsa, d&b
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
4. the person watching zombie movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | zombie     | satire |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | funk | d&b    |

