.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, baking, fishing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, electronic, folk
1. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is the fan of electronic##1
4. the fan of rock is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | fishing | traveling   | baking |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | rock | folk      |

