.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, sprite
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, pakistani, turkish
1. the turkish is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | water | sprite |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | turkish          | canadian |

