.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, pony, cat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | pony  | cat   | bird |
| Sport   | swimming | cricket | climbing       |

 